OL,3,C'Substantial disruption' expected
OL,4,Cahead of weekend motorway closure
OL,6,FDrivers are being warned to expect
OL,7,Fdisruption and allow extra time for
OL,8,Ftheir journeys ahead of a full weekend
OL,9,Fclosure of the M4.
OL,11,FThe motorway will be closed in both
OL,12,Fdirections between junction 18 for
OL,13,FBath and junction 19 for Bristol from
OL,14,F7pm on Friday 21 March until 6am on
OL,15,FMonday 24 March, to allow the A432
OL,16,FBadminton Bridge to be demolished.
OL,18,FNational Highways said the bridge,
OL,19,Fwhich was built nearly 60 years ago,
OL,20,Fneeds to be replaced after cracks
OL,21,Fappeared in the structure.
