OL,3,C'Substantial disruption' expected
OL,4,Cahead of weekend motorway closure
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the organisation
OL,7,Fsaid: "This is one of the southwest's
OL,8,Fbusiest sections of motorway. We
OL,9,Fexpect the closure will cause
OL,10,Fsubstantial disruption.
OL,12,F"If possible, please avoid driving on
OL,13,Fthe M4 round Bristol during the
OL,14,Fclosure. If you have to travel, allow
OL,15,Fplenty of extra time for your journey
OL,16,Fusing signed diversion routes."
OL,18,FThe official diversion takes drivers
OL,19,Fsouth of the M4 through Emerson's
OL,20,FGreen, Warmley and Wick.
